Ļ"We Span Time Together.
We Span Time Together As A Couple.
'Cause We're A Loving Couple. Spanning Time."
Dedicated In Loving Memory Of
PETER HAN-REN McKEAND
31.03.1998 - 12.10.2011"ľ
ĻIN LOVING MEMORY OF
KATHLEEN MILLICAN (KRIS)
1951-2021
WHO LOVED KEW GARDENS.

GONE ARE THE DAYS WE USED
TO SHARE. IN OUR HEARTS
YOU ARE ALWAYS THERE. SO
SADLY MISSED AND LOVED."Ņ
